{"tid":1534402,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Truth behind the 831 Prince Edward MTR terrorist attack","createTime":"2019-09-03T03:47:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T00:37:25.000Z","uid":310864,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"09009a8b2fdab627220deae4567102a589b8de5d","tid":1534402,"uid":310864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:47:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/724119284717359/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia%2Fvideos%2F724119284717359%2F&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFIhgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=1ac38b36\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/724119284717359/</a><br />\n\t<br />\nThe key of this video starts at 6:40.<br />\n<br />\nAt that moment, there was a female shouting<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「醒！醒呀！」</span></span>, which means &ldquo;Wake up! Wake up!&rdquo; when translated.<br />\n<br />\nThe journalist who was recording followed the voice and came across an abnormal scenario where uniformed terrorists are heavily guarding (with firearms) the place which the unconscious or possibly dead person is located.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OL5PA7w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOL5PA7w.png&h=71b012ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nThe uniformed terrorists&rsquo; facial expressions are nervous and panicking.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/491jdUq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F491jdUq.png&h=a7711544&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oENKp1c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoENKp1c.png&h=ef94a9b5&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n<br />\nWhen you hear &ldquo;Wake up!&rdquo; Or &ldquo;Please don&rsquo;t &lsquo;sleep&rsquo;!&rdquo;, you know something terrible has happened, this is common sense.<br />\n<br />\nThe last thing that I would like to mention is that, the Facebook page &ldquo;HA Secrets&rdquo; is an unofficial Facebook page after all, and information from this page will not always be true and accurate.<br />\n<br />\nAnyone with a valid Facebook account will be able to DM them information and the administrator(s) of the page can choose to believe and publish the information that they received at their own will. Therefore what you saw on that page may or may not be fact-checked.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Wake up!&rdquo; That we heard in the above video is already a key and a hint that leads to what the uniformed terrorists are trying to coverup after this incident... Keep your focus and do not get distracted by false information that the terrorists are spreading.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">對唔住，我英文唔太好，只係想有多啲外國人知道香港發生左咩事，有翻譯錯嘅請屌細力啲。。。<br />\n<br />\n(同原po有少許出入，請見諒）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n原po link 後補。</span>"},{"pid":"0b288c48628f358114f90057d01a27ecf53163a5","tid":1534402,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:49:31.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月8！到時見！</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e84bf4d59c3a6ee71df75bdb3b4ff8fd7d1a7fb6","tid":1534402,"uid":310864,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:52:02.000Z","msg":"P 牌求幫推，要比外國人/外媒睇到！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9447261e8bd1e1502876f3d324e4275c4d8f2c24","tid":1534402,"uid":79402,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:27:00.000Z","msg":"tui!"},{"pid":"dacfb6e27bebb42cfe5991f95030c9faffd06b3d","tid":1534402,"uid":112433,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime